GIT STAGES :-

WORKING DIRECTORY :
STAGGING AREA : 
LOCAL REPOSITORY :

===========
WORKING DIRECTORY : WHENEVER CREATE ONE FILE AUTOMATICALLY FILE ENTER INTO WORKING DIR .
--> WORKINNG DIR FILES ALWAYS SHOWS RED COLOUR 
HOW TO CHECK ?
GIT STATUS 

STAGGING AREA : WHEN PERFORMS "GIT ADD " THEN AUTOMATICALLY FILES COMES INTO  WORKING DIR TO STAGGING AREA
STAGGING AREA FILES SHOWS GREEN COLOUR --> GIT STATUS

LOCAL REPOSITORY :- WHENEVER EXCUTE GIT COMMIT -M "<MESSAGE>" COMMAND AUTOMATICALLY FILES COMING FROM STAGGING TO LOCAL REPO
 --> WHEN WE ARE USING GIT PUSH COMMAND 
REMOTE REPOSITORY 

